{
  "stem": "18802.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 417.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I took his orders.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he was very glad and very content that it worked out so nice.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I found out after two months what sell best is bijoux, some necklace or a pin or pair of earrings-- much better the hostess was more-- I see-- glad to get it than piece, box of chocolate.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So how do you get these things?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And now, the war has started.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "There was nothing to buy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And as I had a hobby as a girl, I made always necklaces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So I went to Bethlehem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I found an old Arab who was very nice.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And I told him what I want to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he-- I said, I would like to buy rosary, rosaries, all kind of rosaries, yeah?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I will make necklaces out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Do you mind?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "He said, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Business is business.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He had no religious-- I mean, no idea that is a-- first of all, he was no Christian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "Anyway, I bought a few rosaries, different things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I bought some kind of grains, you see.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In German, it's [SPEAKING GERMAN] How would you say?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "This-- they are brown sticks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I don't know what you call it in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You don't know either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, I bought different grains.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I made necklaces of rosaries and of grains for sporty dresses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They looked very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they sold perfect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And after a few months, I decided only to have bijouterie.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started to manufacture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was really the beginning of our wealth in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I, I left this guy because I needed a bigger showcase.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I opened a store opposite, yes?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I even made in the a newspaper a competition.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
